// Regression bench: contains-chain x 200 fns — confirmed Agent 8 trigger pattern
// Related: shared/hexa/interpreter_fixes_20260411.json#FIX-NESTED-IF
// Pattern: if text.contains(a) || text.contains(b) || ... (10 terms) { return "tag" } x 4 ifs x 200 fns
// Hypothesis: type inference re-visits all early-returning string fns per new fn -> O(N^~1.8)
// Measured: bench=0.156s baseline=0.011s ratio=13.58x (date 2026-04-11, rust native hexa)
// Sweep: N=100 ratio=3.2x; N=200 ratio=13.6x; N=400 ratio=14.7x — clear super-linear
// supersedes negative repro 9a5e78c (lacked || + .contains())

